Package org.apache.struts.validator.validwhen

Class ValidWhenBaseVisitor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
      • org.apache.struts.validator.validwhen.ValidWhenBaseVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParseTreeVisitor<T>, ValidWhenVisitor<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ValidWhenEvaluator
    public class ValidWhenBaseVisitor<T>
extends AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements ValidWhenVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of ValidWhenVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
